   <head>An aduertisement to the devout Reader, vpon the vse of the fiue SENSES.</head>
   <p>LEnd here thine <hi>eare</hi> of zealous atten<gap reason="illegible" extent="1 letter">
         <desc>•</desc>
      </gap>ion, fixe here thine <hi>eye</hi> of inward contemplation, that following the <hi>sauour</hi> of thy Sauiours oyntments, and <hi>tasting</hi> how sweet he is in goodnes, thou may vnfainedly be <hi>touched</hi> with remorse of conscience. Farewell.</p>
